陳伯尋晚為咗我地係防線擋住班狗<br />\n班狗實唔Gur想咬返佢<br />\n海富已經比人掉樽啦！<br />\n年輕人 今日同我出黎保護返陳伯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3xWp4F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3xWp4F.png&h=2be2eefa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［陳伯吹雞 聽日要人］陳伯絕食咗288個鐘 佢今日出黎係為咗保護年輕人跪係警察防線前<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[連登動新聞上線啦] 新聞唔報連登報 &mdash; 絕食266小時陳伯吹雞要人！！和理非及記者必入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1314671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1314671</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[沙田戰線]陳伯:你話比我聽邊個地方最危險, 我要去嗰度保護啲年輕人!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317227</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[求助要人]海富73歲陳伯已絕食9日超過200小時 隻腳有傷口未埋口 點解無人知無人理！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctLg5Dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctLg5Dd.png&h=b751ccda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90971d4320e1a7ccfcbdd70f09492aee33da7008","tid":1319732,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7afb5edeaaed160aa1354e9f32f3a49b5f48ad","tid":1319732,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3558f1f44bab88daac40b54aa8eaf6b251de59","tid":1319732,"uid":16279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"Lm"}]}